overview: A personal quest for inner salvation, we witness a shaman intent on oblivion through Clubland, a desert drifter get's in touch with a purer world after escaping a violent cult - a nymphomaniac develops pregnancy addiction - while a philosopher and preacher descended into the madness of an existential demon psyche. All are a springboard into the hysteria of the other side and the cost of being reborn
title: Pregnant
